{"chroma:document":"VPN Connection Issue Solution:\n\nIf VPN is not working or not connecting:\n\n1. Check your internet connection\n2. Restart VPN application\n3. Re-enter your VPN username and password\n4. Try connecting to another VPN server\n5. Restart your system\n\nIf VPN still does not connect:\n- Contact IT support\n- VPN server may be temporarily down\n- Your VPN access may have expired"}